patterns: how far is hostel from college

Some key details about the hostels: The university has separate hostels for boys and girls, with modern amenities like Wi-Fi, laundry, 24/7 security, and recreational facilities. patterns: does the veltech have a library facility
responses: Vel Tech Rangarajan Dr. Sagunthala R&D Institute of Science and Technology boasts spacious and well-equipped libraries for different departments. The central library for the School of Computing is located in Block 21 on the third floor, the central library for the School of Electrical & Communication is in Block 22 on the third floor, the central library for the School of Mechanical & Construction is in Block 23 on the third floor, and the central library for the School of Management of Basic Science is in Block 24 on the third floor.
